query:
SELECT
        	users.email AS email,
        	(uptime * $1 + CAST(tasks_count as DOUBLE PRECISION) * $2) AS points,
        	COUNT(users_ip.id) AS ips
        FROM
        	daily_stats
      		JOIN users ON users.id = daily_stats.user_id
      		JOIN users_ip ON users.id = users_ip.user_id
        WHERE
            day = $3
        GROUP BY
	        users.email,
	        points
        ORDER BY
        	points DESC
        	LIMIT $4
